ChangeList.Description: Added the **accessReviewHistoryDecisionFilter** enumeration type.
Added the **accessReviewHistoryStatus** enumeration type.

Added the [accessReviewHistoryScheduleSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryScheduleSettings?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type. Use this resource to configure the settings of an [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistorydefinition?view=graph-rest-1.0) object.

Added the [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryDefinition?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Represents a collection of access review historical data and the scopes used to collect that data.

Added the [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource and related methods. Represents the instances of a recurring access review history definition.
Added the **historyDefinitions** relationship to the [accessReviewSet](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewSet?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [generateDownloadUri](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accessreviewhistoryinstance-generatedownloaduri?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryInstance?view=graph-rest-1.0).

Added the **decisionHistoriesForReviewersEnabled** property to the [accessReviewScheduleSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewschedulesettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Indicates whether decisions on previous access review stages are available for reviewers in a multi-stage access review.

Added the **stageSettings** property to the [accessReviewScheduleDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewscheduledefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Defines the stages and their settings in a multi-stage access review.
Added the **stages** relationship to the [accessReviewInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [accessReviewStageSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewstagesettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Exposes the properties used to configure stages and their settings in a multi-stage access review.

Added the [accessReviewStage](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewstage?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type and associated methods. Represents a stage in an [accessReviewInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstance?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added the **accessReviewStageFilterByCurrentUserOptions** enumeration type.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAccessPackageAssignmentPolicyResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAccessPackageAssignmentPolicyResource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. This resource represents an access package assignment policy for which access is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-beta) object.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAzureRoleResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAzureRoleResource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. This resource represents Azure resource roles for which access is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-beta) object.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemServicePrincipalResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemServicePrincipalResource?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. This resource represents service principals whose access to a resource is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-beta) object.
Added the **instance** relationship to [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [recordAllDecisions](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/recordAllDecisions?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAccessPackageAssignmentPolicyResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAccessPackageAssignmentPolicyResource?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type. This resource represents an access package assignment policy for which access is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) object.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAzureRoleResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemAzureRoleResource?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type. This resource represents Azure resource roles for which access is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem]((https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) object.

Added the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemServicePrincipalResource](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItemServicePrincipalResource?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource type. This resource represents service principals whose access to a resource is represented through an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem]((https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-1.0) object

Added the [accessReviewReviewer](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewReviewer?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [accessReviewHistoryScheduleSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistoryschedulesettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Use this resource to configure the settings of an [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistorydefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) object.
Added the **scheduleSettings** property to [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryDefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **instances** relationship to [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryDefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Represents the instances of a recurring acecss review history definition.
Added the [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewHistoryInstance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Deleted the **downloadUri** property from the [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistorydefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use the **downloadUri** property in the [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistoryinstance?view=graph-rest-beta) object instead.

Deleted the **fulfilledDateTime** property from the [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistorydefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use the **fulfilledDateTime** property in the [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistoryinstance?view=graph-rest-beta) object instead.

Changed the bindingParameter and return type of the **generateDownloadUri** action from an [accessReviewHistoryDefinition](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistorydefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) object to an [accessReviewHistoryInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/accessreviewhistoryinstance?view=graph-rest-beta) object.
Added the **userSignInRecommendationScope** enumeration type.

Added the [accessReviewRecommendationInsightSetting](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewRecommendationInsightSetting?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. This is an abstract type that exposes resources for configuring the type of insights to provide to reviewers and access review decision-makers.

Added the **recommendationInsightSettings** property to [accessReviewScheduleSettings](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewScheduleSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this property to configure insights that aid reviewers of an access review to make decisions.

Added the [userLastSignInRecommendationInsightSetting](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userLastSignInRecommendationInsightSetting?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Use this type to configure insight settings based on the user's last sign-in date and time into a tenant or application.

Added the **insights** navigation property to the [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [governanceInsight](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/governanceInsight?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. This is an abstract type that exposes resources for configuring the type of insights to provide to decision-makers in an accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem.

Added the [userSignInInsight](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/userSignInInsight?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Use this type to configure insights for an [accessReviewInstanceDecisionItem](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstancedecisionitem?view=graph-rest-beta) based on the user's last sign-in date and time.

Added the [update](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/accessreviewinstance-update) operation to the [accessReviewInstance](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/accessreviewinstance?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource. This operation allows updating the **reviewers** and **fallbackReviewers** properties of an **accessReviewInstance**.
